strings:
<se_low>Yangus: This ain't right!
We ain't done nuffin'!
Let us out of 'ere!

<se_low>King Trode: I am royalty! A king!
I am most certainly not a monster!
The cheek of that impertinent swine!
<se_high>Jessica: There's no point kicking up a fuss. We've got to think of a way to get out of this cell.
<se_high>Jessica: Haven't you got any bright ideas, <hero>?

<voice_0x01000BDB><se_def>Angelo: Good evening, everyone!
Glad to see you're all looking so well!

<voice_0x01000BDD><se_def>Angelo: Now, now! Control your temper!
I must apologise for before.
Perhaps you will accept this as conciliation?

<voice_0x01000BDF><se_def>Angelo: The guard upstairs might hear if we talk now.
I'll explain later. Come on!
